{"tid":2291396,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大學生發起校內遊行 ， 但無法控制警方是否介入","createTime":"2020-11-18T17:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T05:30:36.000Z","uid":219007,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b43d3da75b82fd42b57ecf179ca04b08d76d01fd","tid":2291396,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PfMU8YCSldHY2HXDhGWAXsNAmZM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VIXI2T5JZ5GIXNGBGSSYDLW4FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPfMU8YCSldHY2HXDhGWAXsNAmZM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVIXI2T5JZ5GIXNGBGSSYDLW4FQ.jpg&h=926f6949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大上星期指因應疫情，原定於明天（19日）舉行的畢業禮將改於網上舉行。有中大學生發起校內遊行，除不滿校方基於政治考慮，取消實體畢業禮，亦紀念去年的社會運動，以及表達對近月政府強行推港區國安法、取消議員資格等的不滿。其中一名發起人表示，無法控制警方是否介入，但預計活動會和平舉行。<br />\n<br />\n該活動的宣傳訊息在社交媒體流傳，呼籲畢業生及學生自備文宣，在星期四（19日），即原定舉行畢業禮的日子，從民主女神像前遊行至百萬大道，並會途經去年發生激烈衝突的二號橋。活動簡介指，政府今年以防疫爲名打壓自由，大學生面對社會不公應「勇敢説不」，繼承在去年社會運動中傷亡者及12名被扣押在內地的港人的意志，表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n發起人：能力範圍內做到最好<br />\n<br />\n有不願具名的發起人表示，不滿校方以防疫為由，將畢業禮改為網上舉行，認為有政治考慮，「本身12月有好多考試都仲係要face to face（面對面），甚至有好多課程都陸續變返面授」，故認為有必要舉行一個「現實嘅畢業禮」。<br />\n<br />\n「（警方）介唔介入都理唔到㗎啦，盡量喺能力範圍內做到最好就算。」發起人指預計活動會和平進行，「我地嘅intention（動機）只係一個畢業禮嚟，但唔反對同學喺途中對任何人反映任何意見。」<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會會於同日傍晚舉行《中文大學保衛戰》紀錄片放映分享會，參加者須先填妥網上表格，不設現場報名。<br />\n<br />\n中大校方昨（17日）回覆查詢時指，大學自年初起籌備網上及實體畢業禮，因近日確診個案有上升趨勢，評估健康風險後宣佈典禮於網上進行。回覆又指大學成員在校園內須遵守《預防及控制疾病條例》 下的規定，如有違反規定及「危害公衆健康及安全」的行爲，大學必須「嚴正處理」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/ET2QWABGDJERPHU7DKYEXNKG2U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WdBUGP3aHjmiPywFnFgiEI8IvjCOV2fh7JaM1TYNR8A-O2vorsCkveLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FET2QWABGDJERPHU7DKYEXNKG2U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1WdBUGP3aHjmiPywFnFgiEI8IvjCOV2fh7JaM1TYNR8A-O2vorsCkveLw&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5qha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=fef03e05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FET2QWABGDJERPHU7DKYEXNKG2U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1WdBUGP3aHjmiPywFnFgiEI8IvjCOV2fh7JaM1TYNR8A-O2vorsCkveLw&h=2890d180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/ET2QWABGDJERPHU7DKYEXNKG2U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WdBUGP3aHjmiPywFnFgiEI8IvjCOV2fh7JaM1TYNR8A-O2vorsCkveLw</a>"},{"pid":"2ee9b35435d9475b94a74a4079565c8a9022b0fe","tid":2291396,"uid":143499,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6743bebfaf49c843ee7073afca63707b4b021b3a","tid":2291396,"uid":266519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"成個靈堂咁"},{"pid":"716d2944f941b567d69180838f1c9cbbb195becd","tid":2291396,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4925f277609d3d85c7cc37885a56904ad3d5fe","tid":2291396,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"無警察咪和平囉"},{"pid":"312eed9d84298917535d5fd838a5e1d2201914a7","tid":2291396,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d7c75d1693a3561f766511612f5f033a3dd22b8","tid":2291396,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T0